ERI - low back fit flare dress - deep sky(34) flare dress - deep sky <p>The deep-sky blue Eri dress is a timless choice for summer. It's cut to a fit and flare silhouette with boxy pleats at the waist and a square-shaped low back. Take it from day to night with a simple switch of shoes, adding a cross-body bag for the most effortless of transitions.</p>